Title: Classification of Meronymy by Methods of Relational Concept Analysis  
Author: Uta E. Priss 
Address: 1, Schlogartenstr. 7, 64289 Darmstadt  
Affiliation: TH-Darmstadt, Fb 4, Ag  
Abstract: This paper introduces a method for classifying the meronymy relation based on quantificational tags. It is an example for an application of Relational Concept Analysis, which is an extension of Formal Concept Analysis, in the field of computational linguistics. Therefore this paper does not report the complete results of an investigation, but it tries to give ideas for further research using these methods.
